# A jQuery plugin to colorize your page via options curated by you :)

## Options
	* choose the color input 
	* select the property being changed (the property must have a color input, such as background, color, fill, etc.)
	
## Defaults
	* this plugin defaults to the colors used on unakravets.com
	* the default property changed is 'color'

## Example
 $('.className').colourify({
	colors: ['#4eb19d','#f32047','#02f7c6', '#bab8ef'],
	property: 'background-color'
	});

This is for those indecisive people who still want to have a little bit of control. 